            <title><![CDATA[【[吃惊][裂开]长期横向刷牙可能会导致牙齿缺损】 同济大学附属口腔医院院长王佐林表示，横向刷牙是刷牙最不好的一个方式🙅🏻不仅会导致牙齿缺损、牙龈萎缩...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>长期横向刷牙可能会导致牙齿缺损】 同济大学附属口腔医院院长王佐林表示，横向刷牙是刷牙最不好的一个方式🙅🏻不仅会导致牙齿缺损、牙龈萎缩，还可能会使牙齿折断！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>阿卫提醒，以后刷牙，要记得使用巴氏刷牙法，保护牙齿<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[嘻嘻]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_xixi-643ef6e48d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4987253902999585" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hlk3bew21xj20k00zk75x.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/AAd1nkS6lx08bx4KQdgc01041200amup0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704716256&amp;ssig=afhd6FEd8Q&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/v6GfJj7ylx08bx4KyVnG010412006ah90E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704716256&amp;ssig=zmFBFarPxP&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/d1TEB101lx08bx4KqPwk010412003jZt0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704716256&amp;ssig=hIBmL%2BtOa1&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4987253902999585" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
