        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[卫宝们周末愉快[微风] 大家起床了吗？[磕到了] 一个小问题，你们刷牙后会把牙刷头罩起来吗？#把牙刷头罩起来会更卫生吗# [疑问]⭕️“裸放”牙刷[星星]细菌主要...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[卫宝们周末愉快<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[微风]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/w_weifeng-6dce9bef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 大家起床了吗？[磕到了] 一个小问题，你们刷牙后会把牙刷头罩起来吗？<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8A%8A%E7%89%99%E5%88%B7%E5%A4%B4%E7%BD%A9%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%E4%BC%9A%E6%9B%B4%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8A%8A%E7%89%99%E5%88%B7%E5%A4%B4%E7%BD%A9%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%E4%BC%9A%E6%9B%B4%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#把牙刷头罩起来会更卫生吗#</span></a> <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>⭕️“裸放”牙刷<br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>细菌主要来自口腔正常菌群，环境恶劣、口腔卫生不佳会增加致病菌数量；<br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>主要是致病力弱的细菌。<br><br>⭕️“戴套”牙刷<br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>细菌来源与“裸放”基本一致；<br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>适合细菌生长，致病力强的细菌数量显著增加。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>结论就是：用完牙刷，把水分尽量甩干，放在干净的地方就可以了，用牙刷套反而画蛇添足。如果出远门，也最好先把牙刷充分干燥后再装上牙刷套。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（科普中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hlkun7dimcj20sg0sewge.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
